(47, 4, 2, 45, 1, 16, 16, 'manifestation of the truth', 'Connection of Truth and Power', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of truth in the proclamation of the gospel. 2 Corinthians 4:2 speaks to handling the word of God truthfully, while Romans 1:16 highlights the gospel''s power for salvation, suggesting that truth is foundational to its effectiveness.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
