(47, 4, 3, 47, 3, 14, 14, 'it is hid to them that are lost', 'Blinded Minds and Hidden Gospel', 'This connection highlights the theme of spiritual blindness affecting understanding. Both passages emphasize how a lack of revelation leads to the gospel being ''hid'' from those who are lost.', 'theme', 0.43299999999999994, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
