(47, 4, 3, 40, 11, 25, 25, NULL, 'Connection of Hidden Knowledge', 'This connection highlights the theme of knowledge being hidden from certain groups. Both passages emphasize that the gospel and divine truths are concealed from the wise and prudent, while being revealed to those who are humble or ''babes.''', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
