(47, 11, 10, 45, 1, 9, 9, NULL, 'Connection of Prayer and Boasting', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of serving God and expressing faith. In 2 Corinthians, Paul boasts about his commitment in Achaia, while in Romans, he highlights his constant prayers, showing a deep connection to his mission.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
