(47, 11, 10, 44, 18, 27, 27, 'regions of Achaia', 'Connection of Achaia and Boasting', 'This connection highlights Paul''s emphasis on Achaia in both passages. In 2 Corinthians, he boasts about his work there, while Acts describes the support he received from the brethren in Achaia.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
