(47, 11, 11, 43, 21, 17, 17, 'God knoweth', 'Connection of Love and Knowledge', 'This connection highlights the theme of love and the knowledge of God. In both passages, the acknowledgment of love is central, with Paul asserting God''s knowledge of his love and Jesus questioning Peter about his love, emphasizing the relational aspect of love and divine awareness.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
