(47, 12, 13, 46, 9, 6, 6, 'not burdensome to you', 'Connection of Apostolic Authority', 'Both passages emphasize the authority of apostles like Paul and Barnabas regarding their right to financial support. The mention of not being burdensome in 2 Corinthians relates to the power to forbear working in 1 Corinthians, highlighting their roles in the church.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
